It's Peter.


74
00:07:36.403 --> 00:07:38.519
Peter D. Carter. “D” is for David.

75
00:07:38.613 --> 00:07:40.675
Squadron Leader Peter Carter.
No, I'm not going to land.


76
00:07:40.699 --> 00:07:43.066
Undercarriage is gone,
inner port's on fire.


77
00:07:43.159 --> 00:07:45.116
I'm bailing out presently.
I'm bailing out.


78
00:07:45.912 --> 00:07:47.698
- <i>Take a</i> telegram.
- Got your message.


79
00:07:47.789 --> 00:07:49.871
