We can hear you.

80
00:07:49.958 --> 00:07:51.790
<i>Telegram to my mother.</i>

81
00:07:51.876 --> 00:07:55.790
<i>Mrs. Michael Carter,

82
00:07:55.880 --> 00:07:57.416
88 Hampstead Lane, London.

83
00:07:59.467 --> 00:08:01.174
Tell her that I love her.

84
00:08:01.261 --> 00:08:04.174
