- Why not?


194
00:16:10.374 --> 00:16:15.460
There's no smoke without fire,
and we don't call smoke holy.


195
00:16:17.089 --> 00:16:19.501
Thanks for the gin, 
Section Officer.

196
00:16:20.051 --> 00:16:22.759
Boy, oh, boy! Home was nothing like this!

197
00:16:25.515 --> 00:16:27.131
Mine was.

198
00:16:33.272 --> 00:16:34.808
Sign here.

199
00:16:35.566 --> 00:16:38.729
